RasterFunctionTemplate.Name: rvt_esri_slrm
RasterFunctionTemplate.Description: RVT Simplified local relief model. Calculates Simplified local relief model.
RasterFunctionTemplate.Help: Local relief modelling removes the large scale morphological elements (hills, alleys…) from data so only small scale features remain (e.g. archaeology). This version of the tool uses a simplified process – the trend is computed by a simple mean filter and a trend removed model is produced directly by subtracting the filtered model from the original.
